This is a set of tools for working with wordlists:

bigger			Filter out the lines less than 8 characters long
doubleyo.py		Make two variants for Russian words containing 'yo' characters: both with 'e' and 'yo'
lowercase.py		Turn all words to lowercase
mobilizer.py		Translate words as they could be typed on a mobile phone keyboard
mutation.py		Simple wordlist mutation: all combinations of lower and upper case of characters for each line
tanslit.py		Transliterate Russian words to English
turnlayout.py		Write all Russian words in English layout (incorrect layout effect)
uppercase.py		Turn all words to uppercase

All the Python scripts are intended to work with UTF-8 locale. Please change the sources for you needs.
